Source material
---------------
Synthesized while reading the freely circulated Fortran 2023 working draft
J3/23-007r1 ("Draft Fortran 2023"), an internal working document of
INCITS/Fortran and ISO/IEC JTC1/SC22/WG5.

This skill does NOT reproduce the draft or the published ISO/IEC 1539-1:2023
standard. It expresses, in our own words, the facts and ideas the language
defines — syntax rules, constraints, and feature semantics — which are not
themselves protected by copyright. Verbatim overlap is limited to such
functional elements (keywords, syntax, constraint identifiers), not
explanatory prose.

Not affiliated with, endorsed by, or a reproduction of the Fortran standard.
The authoritative, normative text is the published ISO/IEC 1539-1:2023, available
from ISO. For conformance questions, consult that standard.
